                <div class="version-pill blue"><span>{{ghostVersion}}</span></div>
            </div></h3>
            <p><b>Download</b> a development copy of Ghost, any time!</p>
            <a href="https://ghost.org/developers/" class="button-blue-hollow">Grab the source code</a>
        </article>
